OL,3,CKonnie Huq: Getting children
OL,4,Cinterested in art and culture is 'no-
OL,5,Cbrainer'
OL,7,FTV presenter Konnie Huq has said it is
OL,8,F"really important" to encourage
OL,9,Fchildren to be interested in arts and
OL,10,Fculture, adding: "It's a no-brainer."
OL,12,FThe former Blue Peter star, 51, has
OL,13,Fbacked the 2026 Kids Aloud initiative,
OL,14,Fwhich encourages children and their
OL,15,Fparents to feel welcome in cultural
OL,16,Fspaces such as museums and galleries.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@RO]rD@ROUrD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
