CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784854087
OL,3,CKonnie Huq: Getting children
OL,4,Cinterested in art and culture is 'no-
OL,5,Cbrainer'
OL,7,FThe campaign, on behalf of charity Art
OL,8,FFund, will see over 60 participating
OL,9,Fmuseums across the UK allocate
OL,10,Fspecific hours for children to visit,
OL,11,Fduring which they can express
OL,12,Fthemselves freely and noisily.
OL,14,FIn an interview with the Press
OL,15,FAssociation, Huq explained why she is
OL,16,Fso passionate about the project `
OL,17,Fwhich is in its third year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
