CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784854087
OL,3,CKonnie Huq: Getting children
OL,4,Cinterested in art and culture is 'no-
OL,5,Cbrainer'
OL,7,FShe said: "It is really important to
OL,8,Fget our kids interested in the arts
OL,9,Fand ignite their passion for learning
OL,10,Fat a young age.
OL,12,F"This whole initiative is all about
OL,13,Fthat."
OL,15,FThe mother-of-two continued: "Most of
OL,16,Fus parents know what it's like, having
OL,17,Fa lot of time to kill and bored
OL,18,Fchildren on your hands.
OL,26,@oD@KOUtD@AOUuD@FO]wD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784854087
OL,3,CKonnie Huq: Getting children
OL,4,Cinterested in art and culture is 'no-
OL,5,Cbrainer'
OL,7,F"The worries that parents have are
OL,8,Fthat their kids will be loud or
OL,9,Fdisruptive or disturb other people `
OL,10,Fbut people know it's the summer
OL,11,Fholidays."
OL,13,F"We want young people to be interested
OL,14,Fin the arts, in museums, in galleries,
OL,15,Fin culture, and to be knowledgeable,"
OL,16,FHuq added.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@JO]uD@AOUwD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
