PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784854088
OL,3,CKonnie Huq: Getting children
OL,4,Cinterested in art and culture is 'no-
OL,5,Cbrainer'
OL,7,FMuseums across the UK, such as FE
OL,8,FMcWilliam Gallery in Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fand St Fagans National Museum of
OL,10,FHistory in Cardiff, will hold events
OL,11,Fencouraging kids and their families to
OL,12,Fvisit.
OL,14,FHuq said: "If you can entertain and
OL,15,Feducate (children) at the same time,
OL,16,Fand have activities to do over the two
OL,17,Fmonths or one-and-a-half months of the
OL,18,Fsummer holidays, it's a win-win
OL,19,Fsituation.
OL,26,@vD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
