PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784854088
OL,3,CKonnie Huq: Getting children
OL,4,Cinterested in art and culture is 'no-
OL,5,Cbrainer'
OL,7,F"It's really important, no matter
OL,8,Fwhere you live, to get kids enthused
OL,9,Fabout culture, the arts, knowledge.
OL,10,FIt's a no-brainer, really."
OL,12,FHuq is best known for being on Blue
OL,13,FPeter for 11 years, serving as the
OL,14,Flongest-serving female presenter in
OL,15,Fthe show's history, and she has also
OL,16,Fhosted programmes such as The Xtra
OL,17,FFactor and King Of The Nerds.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
