PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784854088
OL,3,CKonnie Huq: Getting children
OL,4,Cinterested in art and culture is 'no-
OL,5,Cbrainer'
OL,7,FThe broadcaster was joined by Jenny
OL,8,FWaldman, the director of Art Fund, at
OL,9,Fan event at the Foundling Museum in
OL,10,FLondon on Wednesday to launch the 2026
OL,11,FKids Aloud campaign.
OL,13,FMs Waldman told PA: "All of this is to
OL,14,Fsay to parents: It's the summer
OL,15,Fholidays, kids are allowed in museums,
OL,16,Fthey're also allowed to make a noise.
OL,18,F"They're allowed to do things. They're
OL,19,Fallowed to be creative, even messy `
OL,20,Fall of that is part of just getting
OL,21,Fthe museum habit."
OL,26,@uD@UOUzD@AOU}D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784854088
OL,3,CKonnie Huq: Getting children
OL,4,Cinterested in art and culture is 'no-
OL,5,Cbrainer'
OL,7,F"The summer holidays is for kids in
OL,8,Fmuseums, and Kids Aloud is the epitome
OL,9,Fof that," she added.
OL,11,FNew research by Art Fund found that
OL,12,F65% of parents to children under 11
OL,13,Fyears old are too worried or
OL,14,Fembarrassed to take their children to
OL,15,Fmuseums or galleries this summer.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
