OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784854088
OL,3,CKonnie Huq: Getting children
OL,4,Cinterested in art and culture is 'no-
OL,5,Cbrainer'
OL,7,FThe charity also found that 90% of
OL,8,Fparents believe that visiting a museum
OL,9,For gallery is good for their children
OL,10,Fbut 33% expressed concerns around
OL,11,Fnoise and 32% about damaging items
OL,12,Fwhen discussing reasons that may stop
OL,13,Fthem going.
OL,15,FAmong the museums offering family-
OL,16,Ffriendly events this summer are the
OL,17,FBrighton Museum And Art Gallery, Leeds
OL,18,FMuseums and Galleries, The Fitzwilliam
OL,19,FMuseum in Cambridge and Victoria Art
OL,20,FGallery in Bath.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
